To compress the videos:

1. Go to website videosmaller.com

2. upload video

3. check the "use low compression level (best quality)"

4. choose in the "scale (reduce) video width" the option: "scale to 480 width"

5. click upload video and when completed download the video.

For fam videos, it should be around 350 KB. For test trials, it will be around 220 KB
